THIS REPORT WE HAVE MADE FORWARD-LOOKING STATEMENTS. THESE STATEMENTS ARE BASED ON OUR ESTIMATES AND ASSUMPTIONS AND ARE SUBJECT TO RISKS AND UNCERTAINTIES. FORWARD-LOOKING STATEMENTS INCLUDE THE INFORMATION CONCERNING OUR POSSIBLE OR ASSUMED FUTURE

RESULTS OF OPERATIONS. FORWARD-LOOKING STATEMENTS ALSO INCLUDE THOSE PRECEDED OR FOLLOWED BY THE WORDS ANTICIPATES, BELIEVES, ESTIMATES, HOPES OR SIMILAR EXPRESSIONS. FOR THOSE STATEMENTS, WE CLAIM THE

PROTECTION OF THE SAFE HARBOR FOR FORWARD-LOOKING STATEMENTS CONTAINED IN THE PRIVATE SECURITIES LITIGATION REFORM ACT OF 1995.

